trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"></xref> objects which persist in a Windows Address Book.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en mängd <xref href="System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact"> </xref> objekt som finns kvar i en Windows-adressboken.

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructors, since a reference to it is returned by the <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration> class.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen har inga offentliga konstruktorer eftersom en referens till det returneras av <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration>klass.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerCollaboration>

trans-unit.source: Address books that are associated with <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> management include those associated with the host peer and a remote peer.
trans-unit.target: Adressböcker som är associerade med <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>hantering innehåller alla som är associerade med peer som värd och en fjärr-peer.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>

trans-unit.source: Either computer may collaborate with other peers; when a peer is local to the remote peer but not the host peer, it can be added to the ContactManager of the host peer.
trans-unit.target: Endera datorn kan samarbeta med andra likvärdiga. När en peer är lokal till fjärr-peer men inte värden peer-datorn, kan det läggas till ContactManager för peer värden.

trans-unit.source: Certain operations on the ContactManager class, such as <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.AddContact%2A> and <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.DeleteContact%2A>, correlate to the associated operations being performed on the Windows Address book of the remote peer.
trans-unit.target: Vissa åtgärder på ContactManager class, till exempel <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.AddContact%2A>och <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.DeleteContact%2A>, korrelera till de associerade åtgärder som utförs på Windows-adressboken på fjärr-peer.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.DeleteContact%2A> </xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.ContactManager.AddContact%2A>

trans-unit.source: The host peer has access to this persistent storage for <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact> information, which can be associated with the applications in which a peer intends to participate.
trans-unit.target: Värden peer-datorn har åtkomst till den här beständig lagring för <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>information som kan associeras med de program där en peer avser att delta.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerContact>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication> can identify itself as a user of a ContactManager persistent store on a computer.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication>kan identifiera sig själv som en användare av en ContactManager beständiga arkivet på en dator.</xref:System.Net.PeerToPeer.Collaboration.PeerApplication>
